<p>以下为SCP-CN-1569被收容一周后被发现于Sector-CN-7.15的信件，推测与SCP-CN-1569有关</p>
<div class="page">
<p>致狱卒：<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:x-large;">我等知晓了高先生的结局</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:x-large;">并深表遗憾与敬意</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:x-large;">但我等本意并非如此</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:x-large;">仅为提醒他，艺术即献身</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:x-large;">不得道，毋宁死</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:x-large;">但枪，本只是枪而已。</span></p>
</div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>谨问：<br />
<span class="ruby">吾辈已然脱俗？<span class="rt">Are We Cool Yet？</span></span></p>
</div>
</div>
